Titolo: Nemezis: Mysterious Journey III

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Nemezis: Mysterious Journey III (Previously called Schizm 3: Nemezis), is an adventure game developed by Detalion Games (Roland Pantola studio, after Detalion S.C's shutdown), published by PlayWay S.A, powered by Unreal Engine 4, and the sequel to Schizm: Mysterious Journey and Schizm II: Chameleon. Unlike the previous games, the plotline is not authored by acclaimed Australian science fiction writer Terry Dowling. The game was released on 8th of July 2021 on Steam and GoG.com.